Helix angusticollis Martens, 1875a: 2. Martens 1875b : 185; Pfeiffer 1875: 449, 1876: 149, pl. 134, figs 7-10; Gredler 1882 : 175; Heude 1882 : 36, pl. 15, fig. 8;
